name: Get Your Quote
author: Tbi

sections.description:
The wordpress plugin takes your input and provides you vendors.

More about TotalCryptos.com

Get your quote is a wordpress plugin that provides sevices, home services, packages and vendor quotes. The wordpress plugin takes your input and provides you vendors.

Usage

To show default services on your website, use the shortcode [getyourquote service=”moving”]

To display biggest Gainers and Losers, use the shortcode [getyourquote service=”home-security”]

Legal Disclaimer

getyourquote.com is a service provider which focus on various services. getyourquote.com cannot be held liable for any damages, financial losses, or emotional problems due to the use or misuse of our data. Use as directed. Some assembly required. Batteries not included. Requires adult supervision.

Get Your Quote Services

List of Services

  1. Moving services
  2. Painting service
  3. Solar services
  4. Security alarm
  5. Roofer
  6. HAVAC

Core Skills:

  • Programming
  • Project Design
  • Security analysis

sections.installation:
1. Upload the plugin files to the /wp-content/plugins/plugin-name directory, or install the plugin through the WordPress plugins screen directly.
  2. Activate the plugin through the ‘Plugins’ screen in WordPress
  3. Use theGetyourQuote Name in the lest side on screen to configure the plugin
sections.faq:
What if the plugin stops working?

This plugin is supported by get your quote , please visit https://www.getyourquote.com/ for support.

Is there a premium version of the plugin?

Currently, no. Only the free version.
